txt.en: A totem has exploded, damaging the Deeping Wall
Do not allow Dagrí enough time to escape from the wall
Dagrí is fleeing from the battle
The tower winch has been destroyed

The Orc defiler Dagrí has brought his totems of destruction to Helm's Deep. He must be stopped before he is able to cause destruction to all upon the wall and defeated before he can flee from the battlefield.
Dagrí has fled through the culvert

A powerful White Hand defiler, Dagrí, has lead his followers onto the centre wall section at Helm's Deep. Dagrí means to use his totems of destruction and his defiler allies to cause widespread damage to the defenders still standing on the wall. If enough time passes, Dagrí will attempt to flee from the chaos upon the wall.
